Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.12,0:00:29.76,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}吹乾流下的淚珠輕拂而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.76,0:00:39.69,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是誰 對未來都著著一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.87,0:00:48.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝著明天大步邁進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.44,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.48,0:00:57.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}總有一天會覺醒的 真實心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.89,0:01:04.22,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}現在就伸出雙手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.26,0:01:13.93,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在這開始變化的世界 立刻前往探尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.00,0:01:20.74,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牽繫著你的手絕不再分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.94,0:01:23.74,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因為有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.21,0:01:27.74,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找尋的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.66,0:01:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烤得很不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.00,0:01:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美那邊怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.97,0:01:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得很好 真厲害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以先嘗嘗味道喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.57,0:01:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我嘗嘗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.28,0:01:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好吃 做得很成功喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦身女性部隊到達現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來幫忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.29,0:02:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許可能晚了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.72,0:02:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看要擺飾還是做配菜 請儘管使喚我們來做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.13,0:02:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.00,0:02:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊 你不可以碰蛋糕喔 不然不小心摔到地上就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.94,0:02:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼可以說得這麼過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.21,0:02:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-真是危險…\N-對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個人都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.72,0:02:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通知5121部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本機現正位於熊本市上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預計五分後抵達基地 以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.14,0:03:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「第七話  漫長的夜」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不記得了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水 兩點鐘方向！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.60,0:03:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我昏睡了多久？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概一個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼說話這麼小聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有幻獸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.99,0:04:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等我再說明狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這之前先吃藥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.06,0:04:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在你盡量不要動比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.86,0:04:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏頭有藥 味道可能會怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.43,0:04:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過喝下去應該會舒服一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會苦嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的表情就知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.65,0:04:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們被孤立在幻獸群裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主腦大概也在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒看到外面怎麼會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.90,0:05:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的主腦似乎會排放出高濃度的毒氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥服的過濾器還能撐多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大約12個小時左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.61,0:05:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要聽的是現實的判斷 而不是預期的推測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.61,0:05:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以這種濃度來看最多四小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最快的話 大概三個小時就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.69,0:05:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法送出求救訊號 部隊重整再攻擊也還要六小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生還的機率是零嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.93,0:05:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要擺出這種苦瓜臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.14,0:05:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說點樂觀的事情吧 小呆瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.64,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村 雖然狀況極度惡劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.21,0:05:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過還是有機會得救的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你想要用魔法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.38,0:05:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們出去突破幻獸的包圍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒想到你還真會開玩笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是沒想到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.16,0:06:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…有點睏了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快住手笨蛋 冷靜點啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.92,0:06:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-瀨戶口 放開我\N-隻打一拳我不會消氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我、放開我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汝等已經無路可走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.25,0:07:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未來只能永遠臣服於我 在這諂咒之地了結餘生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.82,0:07:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汝等無法伴隨喜悅 迎接旭日之東昇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.00,0:07:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也無法伴隨安詳 目睹夕陽之西下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.27,0:07:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後汝等將活於黑暗 死於黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:08:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在悲慼之地為自身命運嘆息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.01,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕望將為汝等之糧 死則是汝等之歸宿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.09,0:08:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是騙人的吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再次播報剛剛的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.96,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以下是對馬嚴原地區對幻獸作戰犧牲人員的名單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.04,0:08:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-7784部隊 漆原正己18歲\N-這是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-宮井俊一…\N-這是騙人的、騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要入伍服役？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經通過了適性測驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村 我無法認同你的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依你的出身應該可以免除兵役
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-又何必特地要…\N-我想要戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.96,0:08:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要成為HWT駕駛員 跟幻獸戰鬥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.04,0:09:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(第二水壩集中管理室)\N(非相關人員請勿進入)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.72,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.48,0:09:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以露出這麼沮喪的表情喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在孩子面前要有精神一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上又要再度出動了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.48,0:09:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的部隊似乎免除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們少了一機 上頭似乎也很關心這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經轉達給大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 好像讓氣氛又變凝重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.78,0:10:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是朵可憐的玫瑰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.32,0:10:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在森林中的你如今只能枯萎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.46,0:10:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有水 你應該就會嬌艷欲滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人想種在王城的庭園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.67,0:10:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而如今卻沒有立足之地 只能逃到遙遠的彼方土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(五木村村立戶外休閒中心)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.82,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會冷嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說有條毯子會比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我沒有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是水壩的管理處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理處？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.47,0:11:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是控制水門開關的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻獸的狀況怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外面還是有很多只
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是用走的到這嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.69,0:11:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父親曾經告訴過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.09,0:11:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上有好幾個人 曾經只靠一個面罩逃離幻獸群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是指有高僧會來救嗎 那只是謠傳而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活下來的人都說著相同的事惰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.97,0:11:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻獸會反應人類的恐懼跟憎恨的感情而攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.11,0:12:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己之所以會得救 就是要消去心中的恐懼跟憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人的做法都有所不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.62,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例如不讓內心胡思亂想 或是一直對神感恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.23,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過除了高僧以外 活下來的都只有睡著的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.40,0:12:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才讓我吃了安眠藥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害你不高興的話我先道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.27,0:12:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是覺得拿你沒辦法而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你是讀了哪一段經文？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是經文 是童話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,童話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小時候聽過的童話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這樣至少比較像你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,童話是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.56,0:12:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少我就做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我不對幻獸恐懼或是憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你背我的時候我做了個夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時幻獸有反應嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.44,0:13:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我內心一定是充滿了憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.41,0:13:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有認識的人被幻獸殺害嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 我問了不該問的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心就脫口而出…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很抱歉 請你忘記吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.59,0:13:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是同一間中學的學長 比我大兩個年級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.23,0:13:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是那一種喜歡 只是對他有所憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.11,0:13:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我單方面相當尊敬他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.24,0:13:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三年前他在對馬戰死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也是HWT駕駛員嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是諷刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.59,0:13:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最信任我父親公司所開發機體的人竟然死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.86,0:13:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家的事情你應該也有察覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.26,0:13:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村集團的會長就是我父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.01,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽起來你好像很討厭你父親呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.11,0:14:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說是憎恨 他根本不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.68,0:14:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過人類之所以能活下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.68,0:14:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-就是因為芝村集團開發的…\N-多虧了新兵器是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.42,0:14:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為出現望望美這種可憐的人\N這種兵器才會被開發的啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.56,0:14:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道東原望望美的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.13,0:14:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要啟動PBE需要某種能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過擁有這種能力的人很少 所以借助了遺傳工學的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.04,0:14:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村集團集合世界上的孤兒 然後在研究所進行手術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.08,0:14:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些孩子雖然獲得能力 但副作用導致他們停止成長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.79,0:14:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在肉體跟精神還是個孩子時就被編入了各個部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以望望美才會來5121部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.56,0:15:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於芝村集團為了「人類的未來」而犯下的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.74,0:15:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些可憐的孩子們將永遠都是八歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你想說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.34,0:15:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過望望美並不覺得自己可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.31,0:15:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使會悲傷或是哭泣 我想她並不會覺得自己可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的啊 芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.96,0:15:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒有必要因為望望美他們讓自己背負著罪惡感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.97,0:15:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連對外訊號都中斷 代表HWT已經毀損了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.24,0:15:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中和過濾器可以維持多久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.21,0:15:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.58,0:15:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是想這些也沒用的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.54,0:16:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男的我是無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.77,0:16:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過對女性見死不救將會違反我的美學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.61,0:16:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要坐HWT陪我去搭訕嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要自願再出動嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是去搭訕 搭訕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.39,0:16:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有兩台HWT的話 不可能接下PBE任務的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.33,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請求跟其他部隊混編 我想就可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.77,0:16:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然是自願再出動 必須要獲得大家的同意喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪上老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有個請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.09,0:17:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們都寫在臉上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.96,0:17:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-趕快去召集整備小組吧\N-全機整備完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二號機四號機完全正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨時都可以出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美也可以出門囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.67,0:17:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.24,0:17:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕節都還自願出動的笨蛋們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不快給我就位！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找得到的就這些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.48,0:17:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為是民間制的 所以用過就丟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥服的過濾器還能用一小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.69,0:17:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這些防毒面具用完 頂多也只能撐到早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.46,0:17:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果到時部隊沒來 還是自己試著逃生比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 都交給你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.27,0:17:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多虧了你我才能得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況這隻腳讓我變成累贅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.34,0:18:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要丟下我也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.15,0:18:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從沒想過你是累贅 我也不會丟下你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.52,0:18:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通知8331及5121部隊 目前我們位於砥用市上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距離目的地還有30分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.26,0:18:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,班長 在餐廳我太失控了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我不對 抱歉我打了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.04,0:18:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要道歉等任務結束後 而且你活著回來再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.27,0:18:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前言撤回 剛剛我是認真的 因為我非常的火大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.05,0:18:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好黑喔 什麼都看不到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.81,0:18:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.82,0:18:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能看到小志跟小舞在哪就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.47,0:19:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,8331部隊與敵方前鋒部隊接戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.89,0:19:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是8331部隊 已準備好對主腦設置PBE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5121四號機瀨戶口收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後交給我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.32,0:19:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確認主腦已消滅 毒氣濃度急速下降中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是瀨戶口 找到三號機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.82,0:19:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水他們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.36,0:20:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們兩人似乎脫逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有足跡通往水壩的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不覺得水量增加很多嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在找的是速水他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你說我也知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快到有聖誕歌的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小志他們一定在那裏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.09,0:20:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往下游移動中 速水、芝村\N凌晨四點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.16,0:20:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開水壩水門的是速水他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.91,0:20:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通知5121部隊成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已找到速水及芝村兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人看來都很有精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就讓他們返回輸送機上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.46,0:21:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,班長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.29,0:21:47.67,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}最重要的心情 總是過於接近無法傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.97,0:22:00.18,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}擦肩而過時的悲傷 在我的內心緊緊糾結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.28,0:22:06.05,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}雨過天睛 光珠般的雨滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.39,0:22:12.09,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}我將其收集起來 藉以思念你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.39,0:22:19.56,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}沒人知道我將前往何處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.70,0:22:25.66,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}只有明日的風描繪著我的軌跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.11,0:22:31.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}隨著時代變動的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.91,0:22:37.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}即使迷失在困惑裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.82,0:22:43.95,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}也要抱緊這相遇的奇跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.32,0:22:54.20,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}走吧 一同前去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.04,0:23:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美 預告時間到囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.81,0:23:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要吵她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.51,0:23:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.28,0:23:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓她睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.81,0:23:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣真的好嗎？

